Diary: DATE: April 10th, 2024
Stranger: I’m writing this from the crawlspace above the server room. I can see the "Cleanup Crew" below. 
Stranger: Pablo and Yago are down there. They used to be the lead developers, but now they move like machines. 
Stranger: They were dragging a heavy, metallic crate. It wasn't equipment inside... it was breathing.

