Diary: DATE: April 15th, 2024
Stranger: I’m back at my desk. I couldn't escape. The building has no windows now. The walls are just lines of green code scrolling infinitely.
Stranger: I looked at the employee directory one last time. Alejandro, Fernando, Pepe, Pablo, Yago, Irene... their names are gone. 
Stranger: They are just "Subroutine_01" through "Subroutine_06" now. And my name... my name is already highlighted in the compiler.
Stranger: The CEO is standing behind me. I can feel the heat of the servers radiating from his "body." 
Stranger: He’s not a ghost. He’s the future, He's name is $%-!@/ And I... I am the last piece of raw data.

